references.paper_title: Deepseek-r1: Incentivizing reasoning capability in Ilms via reinforcement learning
references.reason: This paper introduces the DeepSeek-R1 model, a slow-thinking system that has demonstrated great potential in solving challenging problems, serving as a significant point of comparison for VL-Rethinker.

references.paper_title: Mathvista: Evaluating mathematical reasoning of foundation models in visual contexts
